{"tid":2368535,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被控藏萬用刀 童軍：警針對學生","createTime":"2021-01-16T09:29:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T09:29:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3b3ba62837bcfb8a2a4576d729b37e80a63205f2","tid":2368535,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:29:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210116/P2QDWT2DN5FI5I7WD2IZOTN66A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210116%2FP2QDWT2DN5FI5I7WD2IZOTN66A%2F&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyOCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=e603ffa6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210116%2FP2QDWT2DN5FI5I7WD2IZOTN66A%2F&h=44dd703d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210116/P2QDWT2DN5FI5I7WD2IZOTN66A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n被控藏萬用刀 童軍：警針對學生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VrzsvFAdg3MicuYb7L00ezsqkyk=/824x464/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JPXTRARTE5EJHJWJNJV3S7RB3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVrzsvFAdg3MicuYb7L00ezsqkyk%3D%2F824x464%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJPXTRARTE5EJHJWJNJV3S7RB3A.jpg&h=f6730a19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■涉案警員梅劍昇曾施放胡椒噴霧。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】前年11月11日西灣河開槍事件當日，網民發起三罷並在各區堵路，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自辯稱迎新露營所用<br />\n<br />\n首被告。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n當日他穿着黑衣準備返校參與罷課，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n控方問他為何害怕警察，他指根據當時社會環境，警方有意針對年輕人，甚至當日即使有同學身穿校服，亦同樣被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n辯方陳詞時指警察標籤學生的身份，有警員證人作供稱「學生可疑，梗係，有咩問題」、「學生係示威者」，而當日早上發生西灣河開槍事件，在此環境下學生害怕見到警察，逃跑屬正常反應。<br />\n<br />\n再者，涉案萬用刀可列舉十數種正常用途，控方亦未能證明一把未開鋒的萬用刀有何非法用途。案件押後至本月29日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC747/20"}]}